[31m-# ====================================================================[m
[31m-# Interfaces to non-Postfix software. Be sure to examine the manual[m
[31m-# pages of the non-Postfix software to find out what options it wants.[m
[31m-#[m
[31m-# Many of the following services use the Postfix pipe(8) delivery[m
[31m-# agent.  See the pipe(8) man page for information about ${recipient}[m
[31m-# and other message envelope options.[m
